item.title: Welder by U-Boat K32
item.dc:creator: fellan
item.content:encoded:
The inspiration behind the creativity of Welder watch was how travelling through space-time would become reality by the year 2075. Most watch brands project their past into the present. Welder is the opposite. It aims to project the future into the present. The name Welder was created to illustrate the welding of emotions between people. The welding of time and space when travelling through space-time is likely to become a reality by 2075.
The welding of the present to the future is the link between us and our posterity. The Welder watch, designed by Italo Fontana, creator also of U-Boat, encapsulates a timeless feature of ageless identity and size. All the watches belong to the same family in its large offering variety. The three-dimensional feature of the dials is a reminder of the layers of space and time between the present and 2075.
Welder is a fusion of elements from 2075 to the present. It encapsulates time, when time and space merge in the future, a scenario where travel in time becomes a reality, hence projecting our creations into the year 2075.
Mineral. Durable mineral crystal protects watch from scratches. Quartz Movement. Case Diameter: 53mm. Water Resistant To 99 Feet.
